data.description: Price Reduced! Owner Will Pay $5,000 Towards Buyer's Closing Costs !   Welcome to 937 Highland Drive, a charming ranch-style home located in a peaceful cul-de-sac in Hinesville, GA 31313. This all-brick home offers 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a 1-car garage. With 1369 sq ft of living space, this home features a cozy wood-burning fireplace in the living room, perfect for those chilly nights. The spacious eat-in kitchen boasts a walk-in pantry, ideal for storage. Enjoy a formal dining area for gatherings. The private fenced backyard is great for relaxing or entertaining. Additionally, the house has a water purification/softener system installed. Conveniently located just 3 minutes from Fort Stewart's back gate, this home is tenant-occupied until the end of May. With no HOA, you'll enjoy the freedom and flexibility to make this your new home sweet home, with easy access to Fort Stewart!
